{
  "stem": "150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her death was truly tragic, not so much because of the fact that she died, but because she developed Alzheimer's about eight years before she died.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after about three or four years, this beautiful, intelligent woman didn't recognize anybody, couldn't talk, had to wear diapers, couldn't sign her name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The weird thing is that from time to time, she could-- she would still get up and sit at the piano and play a tune, which-- automatically, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think that this is probably the most terrible thing in the world, to see a human being becoming a vegetable.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, each time, of course, I forget a telephone number, or each time I can't remember a name or something, I think, oh my god, it's happening, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can only wish and hope that when and if something like that should happen to me, that somebody will take pity on me and put me out of my misery.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know-- I-- that's why I think that Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kevorkian ?] is doing a good thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What are those things that you were telling me that, that were hurting you so much that you don't want to be hurt more by individuals?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's losing people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's losing people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's losing my first wife, who divorced me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She left me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't blame her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I brought it upon myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had become a fanatic with the Soviet Jewry thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I worked all day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My business could have been much better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I could have been much wealthier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the phone would ring every hour of the day and night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the press was there and the TV was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I would develop programs, and I would run things.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
